01:43:15,480 --> 01:43:17,149
Vamos, cara!

1376
01:43:17,190 --> 01:43:19,568
Cara, escute a música, cara.

1377
01:43:19,610 --> 01:43:21,320
Onde posso encontrar
o comandante?

1378
01:43:21,361 --> 01:43:23,989
